---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AdSlot from '../components/AdSlot.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Editorial Policy"
  description="Learn about our editorial standards, content review process, and commitment to providing accurate health information."
>
  <div class="editorial-policy-page">
    <article class="editorial-content">
      <h1>Editorial Policy</h1>

      <AdSlot position="top-page" />

      <section>
        <h2>Our Commitment to Accuracy</h2>
        <p>
          At Paramedical Knowledge Hub, we are committed to providing accurate, evidence-based health
          information that empowers our readers to make informed decisions about their health and
          wellbeing. Our editorial policy reflects our dedication to maintaining the highest standards
          of content quality, accuracy, and responsible publishing.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Content Standards</h2>
        <h3>Accuracy Guidelines</h3>
        <p>
          All content published on our website undergoes a rigorous review process to ensure accuracy
          and reliability. We base our articles on:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Peer-reviewed medical research and scientific studies</li>
          <li>Guidelines from reputable health organizations (CDC, WHO, NHS, Mayo Clinic, etc.)</li>
          <li>Current medical consensus and evidence-based practices</li>
          <li>Expert consultation when necessary</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Review Standards</h3>
        <p>
          Every article is reviewed by our editorial team for:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Medical accuracy and factual correctness</li>
          <li>Clarity and readability</li>
          <li>Appropriate tone and language</li>
          <li>Completeness of information</li>
          <li>Proper sourcing and citations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Source Verification</h2>
        <p>
          We prioritize information from authoritative sources, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Government health agencies (CDC, NHS, WHO)</li>
          <li>Academic medical institutions and research centers</li>
          <li>Peer-reviewed medical journals (PubMed, medical databases)</li>
          <li>Established medical organizations (Mayo Clinic, Cleveland Clinic, etc.)</li>
          <li>Professional medical associations</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          All articles include references to source materials, allowing readers to verify information
          and access additional resources.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Responsible Publishing</h2>
        <h3>Content Updates</h3>
        <p>
          Medical knowledge evolves continuously. We regularly review and update our content to reflect:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>New research findings and medical guidelines</li>
          <li>Updated recommendations from health authorities</li>
          <li>Changes in medical consensus</li>
          <li>Reader feedback and questions</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Each article displays a "Last updated" date to indicate when the content was most recently
          reviewed and revised.
        </p>

        <h3>Editorial Independence</h3>
        <p>
          Our editorial decisions are made independently, based on medical evidence and reader needs.
          We maintain editorial independence from advertisers and sponsors, ensuring that content
          decisions prioritize accuracy and reader benefit.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>E-E-A-T Commitment</h2>
        <p>
          We are committed to demonstrating Expertise, Authoritativeness, and Trustworthiness (E-E-A-T)
          in all our content:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Expertise:</strong> Our content is written and reviewed by individuals with
            knowledge and experience in health and medical topics.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Authoritativeness:</strong> We cite reputable sources and maintain transparency
            about our editorial process.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Trustworthiness:</strong> We clearly communicate our limitations, provide
            disclaimers, and encourage readers to consult healthcare professionals.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Medical Disclaimer</h2>
        <div class="disclaimer-box">
          <p>
            <strong>Important:</strong> All content on Paramedical Knowledge Hub is for educational
            purposes only and is not intended as a substitute for professional medical advice,
            diagnosis, or treatment.
          </p>
          <p>
            Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified health provider with any
            questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical
            advice or delay in seeking it because of something you have read on this website.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you think you may have a medical emergency, call your doctor or emergency services
            immediately.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Corrections and Feedback</h2>
        <p>
          We strive for accuracy, but we recognize that errors can occur. If you identify an error in
          our content or have concerns about accuracy, please{' '}
          <a href="/contact">contact us</a>. We take all feedback seriously and will investigate and
          correct any verified errors promptly.
        </p>
        <p>
          We also welcome suggestions for improving our content, topics you'd like us to cover, or
          questions about our editorial process.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about our editorial policy, content accuracy, or to report concerns, please{' '}
          <a href="/contact">contact our editorial team</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <AdSlot position="bottom-page" />
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .editorial-policy-page {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .editorial-content {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .editorial-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .editorial-content section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .editorial-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #0f172a;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  .editorial-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #1e293b;
  }

  .editorial-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #334155;
  }

  .editorial-content ul {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .editorial-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #334155;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .editorial-content li strong {
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .editorial-content a {
    color: #0891b2;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .editorial-content a:hover {
    color: #06b6d4;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .disclaimer-box {
    background: #fef3c7;
    border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .disclaimer-box p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #92400e;
  }

  .disclaimer-box p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .disclaimer-box strong {
    color: #92400e;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .editorial-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .editorial-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .editorial-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
  }
</style>

